				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				AC is god.<BR>
My wizard can get to 750+ AC when buffed and I remember, just to give you an idea, once exactly 25 swings of a level 51 frog krup wiz meleeing me (counted) so the tanks could get it off with taunts, and I actually survived, 10 misses. Without heals.<BR>
My shadowknight has 500+ ac when buffed by my level 15 cleric friend and I can solo, without pet, or spells, yellow mobs.<BR>
My monk gets to 1050+ ac when buffed by a 49+ cleric and I can defeat a level 54 warrior with dual lam's in my guild in a duel when he doesn't use a discipline =p<BR>
AC is god.<BR>
Everything else for a tank is secondary. Including strength.<BR>
<BR>
--59 Wizard<BR>
--16 Shadowknight<BR>
--50 Monk<BR>
--Torvonnilous
